1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 1=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(Reborn in Ancient Times as the Empress)

4
00:00:55,900 --> 00:00:57,180
(Wangshi Workshop)

5
00:01:00,260 --> 00:01:02,980
(Wangshi Tower. Workshop)

6
00:01:04,250 --> 00:01:05,350
Bring a few more over there.

7
00:01:05,350 --> 00:01:06,120
- Okay.
- Okay.

8
00:01:06,870 --> 00:01:07,400
Tower Master.

9
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:09,680
We now have eight thousand
trained assassins,

10
00:01:09,790 --> 00:01:11,070
twenty thousand suits of armor,

11
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,560
and hundreds of siege weapons.

12
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,150
Also...

13
00:01:13,230 --> 00:01:14,040
Hold on.

14
00:01:14,710 --> 00:01:16,510
Why are you recruiting
so many assassins?

15
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:18,680
And what's
with all this military equipment?

16
00:01:18,790 --> 00:01:19,580
(Li Qingqing, daughter-in-law of the Pan family)
You don't actually think

17
00:01:19,580 --> 00:01:20,430
(Tower Master of Wangshi Tower, a modern finance elite)
I'm planning a rebellion, do you?

18
00:01:20,740 --> 00:01:22,150
(Caiyuan, Li Qingqing's personal maid
and Left Envoy of Wangshi Tower)

19
00:01:22,150 --> 00:01:24,390
Didn't you say that the old emperor
burdens the people with harsh taxes

20
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:26,390
and joins forces
with powerful clans to oppress them?

21
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:28,560
Listen, we're training talented people

22
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:30,230
to protect our own business.

23
00:01:30,510 --> 00:01:31,200
I came here

24
00:01:32,230 --> 00:01:34,480
to make money and enjoy life,

25
00:01:34,710 --> 00:01:37,000
not to work myself to the bone
becoming the next Empress.

26
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,680
The Empress?

27
00:01:39,590 --> 00:01:40,950
It wouldn't be so bad.

28
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,200
What do you mean?

29
00:01:47,100 --> 00:01:48,760
Don't tell me you've already
made an imperial robe

30
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,280
and plan to sneak it onto me.

31
00:01:51,350 --> 00:01:51,840
Enough!

32
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,540
I told you to find

33
00:01:54,550 --> 00:01:56,170
skilled craftsmen who can do business

34
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:57,990
and officials
who truly care about the people.

35
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,710
Yes, Tower Master.

36
00:02:02,070 --> 00:02:03,480
I'd better figure out a way

37
00:02:03,490 --> 00:02:05,500
to make enough money
to support this whole crowd.

38
00:02:07,110 --> 00:02:08,290
Has the Second Prince arrived?

39
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,910
We need him helping us make money.

40
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,710
The Second Prince hasn't arrived yet.

41
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,680
However,

42
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:15,590
the Crown Prince
is already waiting inside Wangshi Tower.

43
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,190
Him again.

44
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:19,190
I'm not seeing him.

45
00:02:19,190 --> 00:02:20,590
I'm still trying to find a way home.

46
00:02:21,470 --> 00:02:23,710
Even though I woke up
as a married woman,

47
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,680
at least my husband
is stationed at the border.

48
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,880
All I want is to make
a fortune and live comfortably.

49
00:02:27,900 --> 00:02:30,500
I'm not about to let that
scheming Crown Prince ruin everything.

50
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,150
Help!

51
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,240
Move aside!

52
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:03,750
(Oh no.)

53
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:06,080
(How am I still running into
that scheming Crown Prince?)

54
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,100
(Zheng Yuanhe,
Crown Prince of Great Yong)

55
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:11,150
Your Highness,

56
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:13,560
you dare kill a court official
in broad daylight.

57
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,430
You have no regard for the law.

58
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:19,190
And you think you're qualified
to lecture me about the law?

59
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:26,880
What are you doing?

60
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,590
(It's her.)

61
00:03:53,590 --> 00:03:54,310
Hey, handsome.

62
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:56,000
(One year ago)
The road is slippery from the snow. Be careful.

63
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:02,000
(Oh no.)

64
00:04:02,430 --> 00:04:04,750
(What if he recognizes me?)

65
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:08,660
Your Highness!

66
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:20,040
Your Highness.

67
00:04:20,310 --> 00:04:21,990
Every corrupt official
has been executed.

68
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:24,800
Take them all and feed them to the dogs.

69
00:04:24,810 --> 00:04:25,560
Yes, Your Highness.

70
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,270
Let's go.

71
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:33,560
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

72
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:37,700
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

73
00:04:38,410 --> 00:04:40,290
♪Your smile♪

74
00:04:40,290 --> 00:04:42,660
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

75
00:04:42,660 --> 00:04:45,560
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

76
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,390
(Perhaps it's because
I can't stop thinking about her.)

77
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,720
(That's why I mistook her.)

78
00:04:55,750 --> 00:04:56,950
(Pan Residence)
My beautiful mother-in-law.

79
00:04:57,870 --> 00:04:59,190
Qingqing's back!

80
00:04:59,190 --> 00:04:59,950
I brought you

81
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:02,070
your favorite roast chicken
and candied hawthorn.

82
00:05:03,190 --> 00:05:04,480
You're so thoughtful, Qingqing.

83
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,680
You silly girl.

84
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:07,190
I didn't see you for half a day,

85
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:08,120
and I was worried sick.

86
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:08,950
Beautiful,

87
00:05:09,310 --> 00:05:11,190
don't say things like that.

88
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:12,950
You'll definitely live a long,
healthy life.

89
00:05:13,290 --> 00:05:14,270
You'll be around forever.

90
00:05:15,070 --> 00:05:15,680
Oh, stop it.

91
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:17,240
Quit teasing me.

92
00:05:17,830 --> 00:05:19,780
(Madam Pan, Pan Yang's mother)
Yang has returned victorious from the northern campaign.

93
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,430
(Li Qingqing's mother-in-law)
He's finally coming home.

94
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,430
Who?

95
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,000
You silly girl.

96
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,240
You must be so excited.

97
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:28,120
My son. Your husband.

98
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,510
He's coming back.

99
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,630
Wasn't it supposed to be three years?

100
00:05:32,630 --> 00:05:33,430
He won a great victory,

101
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:35,060
so His Majesty
granted special permission.

102
00:05:35,070 --> 00:05:36,000
That's wonderful.

103
00:05:38,070 --> 00:05:39,510
(Is the original owner's husband)

104
00:05:39,630 --> 00:05:41,390
(really back?)

105
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:46,000
Master, Madam!

106
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,220
The young master has returned!

107
00:05:50,340 --> 00:05:51,540
(Pan Yang, General
of the Northern Expedition Cavalry)

108
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,620
(Li Qingqing's husband)
Yang

109
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,340
Your unfilial son, Pan Yang,

110
00:05:55,070 --> 00:05:56,070
greets Father and Mother.

111
00:05:56,130 --> 00:05:57,270
You've both suffered because of me.

112
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,750
Good.

113
00:05:58,750 --> 00:05:59,800
My son,

114
00:06:00,190 --> 00:06:01,600
you're finally home.

115
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,870
(Master Pan, Pan Yang's father and Li Qingqing's father-in-law)
Son, were you hurt?

116
00:06:04,390 --> 00:06:05,160
I'm fine.

117
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:06,070
Are you tired?

118
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,390
Hungry?

119
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:09,150
Mother will make you
roasted sweet potatoes,

120
00:06:09,270 --> 00:06:10,000
Dongpo pork,

121
00:06:10,510 --> 00:06:11,160
braised fish,

122
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:12,280
and garlic shoots.

123
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:13,800
All right, dear.

124
00:06:14,330 --> 00:06:16,510
Qingqing hasn't even
had a chance to say anything yet.

125
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,510
You're right.

126
00:06:17,510 --> 00:06:18,160
Qingqing.

127
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,160
Come, Qingqing.

128
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,560
Come here.

129
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:24,000
(What am I supposed to say?)

130
00:06:24,070 --> 00:06:25,190
(This is so awkward.)

131
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:27,600
Hello...

132
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,070
Yang.

133
00:06:36,820 --> 00:06:39,300
(Li Muyan, Pan Yang's mistress)

134
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,480
Everything has been settled.

135
00:06:46,830 --> 00:06:47,270
Good.

136
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:53,120
Your daughter-in-law, Li Muyan,

137
00:06:53,310 --> 00:06:54,480
greets Father and Mother.

138
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,000
You...

139
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:58,950
What...

140
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,600
(You've been cheated on!)

141
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,830
(You got cheated on!)

142
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:14,270
(What kind of plot twist is this?)

143
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,360
(Me?)

144
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,190
(I've been cheated on.)

145
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,000
Yang,

146
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,000
you and Qingqing are already married.

147
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,920
She's been waiting
for you all this time.

148
00:07:23,070 --> 00:07:24,560
How could you do this to her?

149
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:26,800
It's okay.

150
00:07:31,500 --> 00:07:32,370
- Li Qingqing.
- I...

151
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,040
What do you want?

152
00:07:34,270 --> 00:07:35,070
Just name it.

153
00:07:36,430 --> 00:07:37,510
Anything except my heart.

154
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:38,990
As for everything else,

155
00:07:39,270 --> 00:07:40,510
I'll do everything I can.

156
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:45,390
Actually, I...

157
00:07:45,390 --> 00:07:46,000
Qingqing,

158
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:47,510
don't worry.

159
00:07:47,510 --> 00:07:48,560
Your father-in-law and I
have already accepted you

160
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,310
as our daughter-in-law.

161
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,600
That's right.

162
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,120
I...

163
00:07:52,270 --> 00:07:53,390
I'm the head of this family.

164
00:07:53,390 --> 00:07:55,510
I'll stand up for you.

165
00:07:55,510 --> 00:07:57,270
I just want to say

166
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,000
you can't force love.

167
00:07:59,390 --> 00:08:01,270
If Pan Yang has fallen for someone else,

168
00:08:01,630 --> 00:08:03,000
then let them be together.

169
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:05,310
This...

170
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,190
What?

171
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,190
Look at her.

172
00:08:08,190 --> 00:08:10,310
See what you've driven Qingqing to?

173
00:08:10,310 --> 00:08:12,720
Throw this woman out right now!

174
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,480
You...

175
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:16,240
You ungrateful disgrace!

176
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,120
I'll beat some sense into you!

177
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:18,720
No! No!

178
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:19,700
Don't hit him!

179
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:20,430
Calm down.

180
00:08:20,430 --> 00:08:20,870
Move aside.

181
00:08:20,870 --> 00:08:21,600
I'm pregnant!

182
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:23,680
What?

183
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:26,040
(She came with a baby on the way.)

184
00:08:26,270 --> 00:08:27,070
(They're this bold?)

185
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,920
(Is this really ancient times?)

186
00:08:29,630 --> 00:08:31,750
I'm carrying Pan Yang's child.

187
00:08:32,310 --> 00:08:34,320
If you refuse to accept me
as your daughter-in-law,

188
00:08:34,660 --> 00:08:36,120
I'll leave the Pan family right now

189
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,870
and raise this child on my own.

190
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:39,390
Well...

191
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:42,720
Driving out a pregnant daughter-in-law

192
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,790
doesn't seem appropriate.

193
00:08:45,100 --> 00:08:47,060
(Lan Ximei, matriarch of the Li family)

194
00:08:47,270 --> 00:08:48,120
Mom.

195
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,480
Mother.

196
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,320
What did you just call me?

197
00:08:56,670 --> 00:08:57,320
Don't be afraid.

198
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:58,910
I will stand up for you.

199
00:09:06,150 --> 00:09:07,360
Nineteen years ago,

200
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:10,120
your birth mother was nothing more
than Master's concubine.

201
00:09:10,270 --> 00:09:11,910
She had the audacity

202
00:09:11,910 --> 00:09:14,030
to switch you with my daughter, Muyan.

203
00:09:16,300 --> 00:09:17,740
(The witness, Wang Qiumei)

204
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:21,360
Fortunately, the midwife
who delivered you

205
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,510
recorded the birthmark
on Yan's left leg.

206
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,910
That's how we were reunited.

207
00:09:26,270 --> 00:09:26,910
You...

208
00:09:26,910 --> 00:09:28,890
You're just an illegitimate daughter
of the Li family.

209
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:30,480
How could you compare yourself

210
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:32,290
to my Yan,
the Li family's legitimate daughter?

211
00:09:34,390 --> 00:09:35,600
I'm sorry, Qingqing.

212
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:38,840
Mother only told me recently.

213
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:42,480
(How did I end up
in such a ridiculous situation?)

214
00:09:43,150 --> 00:09:44,240
My dear in-laws,

215
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:45,750
this has nothing

216
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:47,240
to do with Qingqing.

217
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:48,910
Since the Pan family

218
00:09:48,910 --> 00:09:51,360
has accepted Qingqing
as our daughter-in-law,

219
00:09:51,380 --> 00:09:52,910
this marriage
rightfully belongs to her...

220
00:09:52,910 --> 00:09:53,480
Father,

221
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:56,360
a fake will always be a fake.

222
00:09:57,910 --> 00:09:58,360
You...

223
00:09:58,370 --> 00:10:00,560
I'm about to enter the court
and receive a noble title.

224
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:03,030
The ancestors of the Pan family

225
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:03,870
would never approve

226
00:10:03,870 --> 00:10:05,750
of my marrying someone of unknown birth.

227
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,200
Seriously?

228
00:10:07,510 --> 00:10:09,440
Do you really think you're such a catch?

229
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,840
Let's dissolve this marriage.

230
00:10:12,510 --> 00:10:13,030
What?

231
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,550
How dare you insult your husband.

232
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:15,390
Bring out the family rules!

233
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:16,750
I...

234
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:17,840
Qingqing.

235
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,870
Qingqing, don't say that.

236
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,270
Li Qingqing,

237
00:10:22,270 --> 00:10:24,790
whether you're pretending to be virtuous

238
00:10:25,550 --> 00:10:27,120
or acting spiteful,

239
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:29,600
you'll never get my attention.

240
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,750
From now on, Muyan will also be my wife.

241
00:10:38,270 --> 00:10:39,600
I don't care about her dowry.

242
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,320
If you can accept her,

243
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,030
I'll consider

244
00:10:43,030 --> 00:10:43,870
visiting you

245
00:10:44,150 --> 00:10:45,360
once or twice

246
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:46,360
each month.

247
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,270
No, thanks.

248
00:10:49,510 --> 00:10:51,120
If you've got that much energy,

249
00:10:51,510 --> 00:10:52,480
I'd be happy

250
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:54,600
to find you eighteen more concubines.

251
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,330
You're nothing but

252
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:57,120
a child-making machine.

253
00:10:57,390 --> 00:10:57,840
You...

254
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,150
How shameless!

255
00:10:59,390 --> 00:11:00,670
You dare speak of shame?

256
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:01,910
You still dare make a scene before me?

257
00:11:01,910 --> 00:11:02,480
A child-making machine!

258
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:03,080
Who are you calling
a child-making machine?

259
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:03,480
Qingqing!

260
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:04,000
You!

261
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,600
I know you've been wronged.

262
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:06,670
As women,

263
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:08,510
- sometimes we have to be like water.
- No.

264
00:11:08,510 --> 00:11:09,870
We have to let things flow past.

265
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:10,720
You jerk!

266
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,270
Get out!

267
00:11:11,510 --> 00:11:12,270
Just you wait!

268
00:11:12,270 --> 00:11:13,080
There, there. Calm down.

269
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,000
You arrogant, self-absorbed fool.

270
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:14,670
Yang.

271
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:15,840
It's okay. Just ignore her.

272
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,120
Mother.

273
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:17,960
Don't be afraid, Yan.

274
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:18,750
I'm here.

275
00:11:19,060 --> 00:11:20,940
(Wangshi Tower)

276
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:27,360
I'm so mad!

277
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:28,480
Pan Yang wasn't even home.

278
00:11:28,490 --> 00:11:30,000
I was the one
supporting the entire Pan family.

279
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,200
And all those Li family businesses,

280
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,430
I was the one who turned them around.

281
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,660
How dare he treat me like this!

282
00:11:34,150 --> 00:11:36,030
Pan Yang actually humiliated you.

283
00:11:36,660 --> 00:11:37,550
Anyone who bullies you

284
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:39,500
is making an enemy
of everyone in Wangshi Tower.

285
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,120
That's right.

286
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:43,870
I'm the Tower Master of Wangshi Tower.

287
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,950
- I've never had to put up with this.
- Exactly.

288
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:47,390
He has to be taught a lesson.

289
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:48,840
Caiyuan,

290
00:11:49,550 --> 00:11:52,000
summon everyone we have
serving in the imperial court.

291
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,550
Doesn't he want to become an official?

292
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:55,880
Then I'll make sure
every path to office is closed to him.

293
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:57,320
Yes, Tower Master.

294
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,360
Roll call.

295
00:12:06,150 --> 00:12:06,970
Ministry of Revenue.

296
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:07,840
Here.

297
00:12:08,260 --> 00:12:09,150
Ministry of Personnel.

298
00:12:09,670 --> 00:12:10,240
Here.

299
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:13,120
Ministry of War, Ministry of Rites,
Ministry of Justice, Ministry of Works.

300
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:13,910
Is everyone here?

301
00:12:14,550 --> 00:12:16,990
- Everyone's here, Tower Master.
- Everyone's here, Tower Master.

302
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:19,440
I've summoned you all today

303
00:12:19,670 --> 00:12:21,080
to discuss one man.

304
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:22,670
Pan Yang.

305
00:12:28,610 --> 00:12:32,000
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

306
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:36,140
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

307
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:38,650
♪Your smile♪

308
00:12:38,910 --> 00:12:41,200
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

309
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:44,880
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

310
00:12:45,340 --> 00:12:48,650
♪Yet I stand before you♪

311
00:12:49,390 --> 00:12:53,220
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

312
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:55,560
♪Though fate tries♪

313
00:12:55,560 --> 00:12:58,140
♪To make us pass each other by♪

314
00:12:58,360 --> 00:13:01,780
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

315
00:13:02,040 --> 00:13:03,670
♪Though time slips by♪

316
00:13:03,670 --> 00:13:05,430
♪As day turns into night♪

317
00:13:05,950 --> 00:13:09,970
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

318
00:13:10,390 --> 00:13:12,770
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

319
00:13:12,770 --> 00:13:14,560
♪Blessed by fate♪

320
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:19,720
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

321
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:22,160
♪Your smiling face♪

322
00:13:22,160 --> 00:13:25,000
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

323
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:28,620
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

324
00:13:29,140 --> 00:13:32,600
♪And wander the world together♪

325
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:33,940
♪Holding you close♪

326
00:13:33,940 --> 00:13:36,480
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

327
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:38,800
♪Your tenderness♪

328
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:41,660
♪Is the brightest moon♪

329
00:13:41,660 --> 00:13:45,360
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

330
00:13:45,880 --> 00:13:49,170
♪Our love will never fade away♪

331
00:13:49,170 --> 00:13:51,630
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

332
00:13:52,160 --> 00:13:56,410
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

